Package: bmfaToolkits
Type: Package
Title: Toolkits for Multiple Bayesian Integrative Factor Analysis 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mavis", "Liang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mavis.liang@example.com")
  )
Description: Lightweight wrappers and post-processing helpers used in the
    'Bayesian Integrative Factor Analysis' tutorial/paper. The package provides
    separate fit_* and postprocess_* functions for multiple backends (e.g.,
    BMSFA, MOM-SS, SUFA, PFA, Tetris, stacked FA, independent FA), plus small
    example datasets and preprocessing utilities. Some backends are optional
    and require installing additional packages from GitHub/Bioconductor.
